data.description: This updated gem is situated within an exclusive, gated community near Sam Houston Tollway and 59. Features 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, an office, game room, media room, and a range of community amenities such as pools, fitness facilities, basketball courts and more. Enjoy the tranquillity of having no back neighbors and a cul-de-sac location. The home boasts an amazing kitchen with recent stainless steel appliances, 42" cabinets, a coffee bar, and a water softener and reverse osmosis filtration system. An open-concept living area from the kitchen to the den, tall ceilings, arched doorways, and large floor to ceiling windows. The large master suite features his and hers sinks, his and hers closets, plus a jacuzzi tub. An energy-efficient home with dual-pane windows and radiant barrier insulation for low energy costs. Commuting downtown is easy, as the home is located a few minutes from Sam Houston Tollway and 59! This is a must-see property in a prime location! Floor plan in pic gallery
